title: Woman in Tuxedo
description: A woman dressed for a formal occasion, wearing a tuxedo.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the woman in a tuxedo emoji embodies sophisticated elegance with her sharp, tailored black suit and crisp white shirt, all rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading. Her confident posture and the subtle, realistic lighting emphasize a sense of professionalism and celebratory flair, making her a perfect symbol for formal events or breaking gender norms in style. This emoji on Apple devices conveys empowerment, success, and readiness for any grand occasion.
